data.title: ASSIST Scholars
data.meta_description: Adam is a dedicated student leader experienced in project planning, classroom management, and mentoring international students. He aims to apply leadership and management skills for collaborative team environments. He is an ancient philosophy reader, music enthusiast (Foo Fighters, Dream Theater).
data.text: The photos on the top section of the home page of this website are from Pomfret, except the classroom photo, which is from Westminster School and the art classroom photo is from Suffield Academy.
